org.eclipse.scada.configuration.infrastructure

Interface MasterImport

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MasterImportImpl

    public interface MasterImport
    A representation of the model object 'Master Import'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Imported Master
    • Id
    • Credentials
    • Import Selector

    See Also:
    InfrastructurePackage.getMasterImport()
